
Steps to load a stage into memory

1. Load the stage manifest from plist resource.
2. Read all tilemap names in the stage manifest.
3. Load the tilemap manifest for each name, from plist resource.
4. Read tileset name from each layer of each tilemap manifest.
5. Read texture name from eahc tileset manifest.
6. Load textures. 
7. Instantiate tilesets from textures and tileset manifests.
8. Instantiate map layers from tilesets and layer manifests.
9. Instantiate tilemap from map layers.